'''Estadio Jose Ramon Flores''' is a multi-use sports complex located in [[Santa Rosa de Lima, La Unión|Santa Rosa de Lima]], [[El Salvador]]. The sports complex is mainly used for its soccer facility. The soccer field is the home field of [[C.D. Municipal Limeño]], a first division soccer team with a capacity of 5,000.
